> with Vorpal if we dont report soon"

Marauder continued to fly, his boosters lighting up the skies as he continued to move. In the distance land began to appear on the horizon, a long strip of islands and land masses. 

"Ahhh, Darkfate"  Marauder intoned darkly, "You fear Vorpal." His words more a statement than question. "Your fear weakens you." 

Marauder banked, bringing the islands into focus as they headed towards them. "If you would conquer the world, you must first conquer yourself." Boosters flared again as he shot forward as he began to slowly drop in altitude, "Come!" He called out after Darkfate, "The begining awaits you!"

(TAG: Darkfate)
